  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2832510/extras/ea50289427a42132ddc658bfb3fd6f95.webp?t=1769963286\" width=136 height=60 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2832510/extras/e9713bc6d3eabc1c5268e4f9aad06b07.webp?t=1769963286\" width=600 height=31 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Esteem is a game that takes you to discover the saga of a little wolf called Laisa and her internal conflicts as she fights to save her village and her friends. How far would you go for your friends? What fears are you able to face to defend what is most important? Find out by living Laisa's experiences in Esteem!!! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The journey begins when your village is attacked by an entity known only as \"The Void\" and takes with it an important relic, the Essence crystal, whose known properties are to keep life in that region sustainable. Now seeing people losing their essence and becoming amorphous people due to a lack of motivation and feelings, Lais will go in search of the stolen relic and discover that all the internal conflict she has had to date has actually prepared her for the most important saga in history. her life!! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Come and have the experience of realizing how self-esteem can help with the challenges we face on a daily basis and understand that even if you have challenges that you have to deal with alone, many of them you can face with the right allies!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2832510/extras/1d4b354d9a4099268f345ce8e76d1740.webp?t=1769963286\" width=182 height=54 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2832510/extras/e9713bc6d3eabc1c5268e4f9aad06b07.webp?t=1769963286\" width=600 height=31 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2832510/extras/4fc8a9401300207cecaf4556161d2b3e.avif?t=1769963286\" width=600 height=336 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2832510/extras/c55548e99d884c9e110926f70c5e02d1.avif?t=1769963286\" width=600 height=336 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Esteem you will have to deal with Laisa low self-esteem. If you leave your self-esteem low, you will have problems throughout the adventure. To keep her self-esteem high, carry out tasks that give her pleasure, such as taking care of animals, helping people and winning battles.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2832510/extras/65eb460ba55c6cda66e6bee4b30352e6.webp?t=1769963286\" width=343 height=55 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2832510/extras/e9713bc6d3eabc1c5268e4f9aad06b07.webp?t=1769963286\" width=600 height=31 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2832510/extras/0f3f527ab5c2d78bb382ac54a6c93f8d.avif?t=1769963286\" width=600 height=336 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect materials so your friend Alice can make rare and exclusive items to help along the way. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2832510/extras/36e853e145a024cb714bc74c31ccebfb.webp?t=1769963286\" width=351 height=59 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2832510/extras/e9713bc6d3eabc1c5268e4f9aad06b07.webp?t=1769963286\" width=600 height=31 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2832510/extras/c50192396fcc7f27f5a1b0257a89c9e9.avif?t=1769963286\" width=600 height=336 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get ready for intense battles where your strategy will determine whether you will emerge victorious or not. But remember that if your self-esteem is low, your chances will be reduced and the difficulty will be greater, after all, fear can be your biggest enemy!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2832510/extras/3a6e5835825baa125cf8b15da38b5f55.webp?t=1769963286\" width=635 height=62 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2832510/extras/e9713bc6d3eabc1c5268e4f9aad06b07.webp?t=1769963286\" width=600 height=31 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2832510/extras/5068ae9fc1b26fcfbbf202b93978f956.avif?t=1769963286\" width=600 height=336 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore and discover hidden areas. They can reveal valuable treasures that can help in the most complicated moments.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2832510/extras/b275db5c5c914c9885ab2f19f23508c5.webp?t=1769963286\" width=319 height=52 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2832510/extras/e9713bc6d3eabc1c5268e4f9aad06b07.webp?t=1769963286\" width=600 height=31 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2832510/extras/2f860d64bf5c654fd14a0d258ce4dd4c.avif?t=1769963286\" width=600 height=336 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combine items to improve your skills, obtain more efficient weapons and rare accessories.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2832510/extras/e9713bc6d3eabc1c5268e4f9aad06b07.webp?t=1769963286\" width=600 height=31 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2832510/extras/ea50289427a42132ddc658bfb3fd6f95.webp?t=1769963286\" width=136 height=60 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2832510/extras/e9713bc6d3eabc1c5268e4f9aad06b07.webp?t=1769963286\" width=600 height=31 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Esteem is a game that takes you to discover the saga of a little wolf called Laisa and her internal conflicts as she fights to save her village and her friends. How far would you go for your friends? What fears are you able to face to defend what is most important? Find out by living Laisa's experiences in Esteem!!! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The journey begins when your village is attacked by an entity known only as \"The Void\" and takes with it an important relic, the Essence crystal, whose known properties are to keep life in that region sustainable. Now seeing people losing their essence and becoming amorphous people due to a lack of motivation and feelings, Lais will go in search of the stolen relic and discover that all the internal conflict she has had to date has actually prepared her for the most important saga in history. her life!! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Come and have the experience of realizing how self-esteem can help with the challenges we face on a daily basis and understand that even if you have challenges that you have to deal with alone, many of them you can face with the right allies!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2832510/extras/1d4b354d9a4099268f345ce8e76d1740.webp?t=1769963286\" width=182 height=54 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared